final_desc: - Tanah liat lainnya :Tanah liat lainnya (tidak termasuk tanah liat dari pos 68.06), andalusite, kyanite dan sillimanite, dikalsinasi maupun tidak; mullite; tanah chamotte atau tanah dinas.;- Other clays :Other clays (not including expanded clays of heading 68.06), andalusite, kyanite and sillimanite, whether or not calcined; mullite; chamotte or dinas earths.
